1.Creating requirements.txt in your code
2.Creating Dockerfile in your code
3.Login using the below command
docker login --username=''
To see list of images
docker images
4.To build the docker images
docker build -t testjob1 .
5.Create repository in docker pub with public access
6.Create the tag
docker tag testjob1 saipriyadarshini/testjob1
(docker tag imagename username/imagename)
7.PUsh the local docker image to docker hub which is public repository
docker push saipriyadarshini/testjob1
